  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p978568/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img height=\"297\" src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/21/9774180b2f8f9323e6e9a00474ca0cd2.jpg\" width=\"527\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;Fargo&rdquo; has rounded out the cast for Season 3 with the additions of&nbsp;David Thewlis, Michael Stuhlbarg, Jim Gaffigan,&nbsp;Scoot McNairy,&nbsp;Karan Soni,&nbsp;Fred Melamed, and&nbsp;Thomas Mann. The actors join previously announced stars&nbsp;Ewan McGregor, Carrie Coon, and Mary Elizabeth Winstead.《冰血暴》第三季将有众星加盟，其中有David Thewlis、Michael Stuhlbarg、Jim Gaffigan、Scoot McNairy、Karan Soni、Fred Melamed还有Thomas Mann。当然还有之前就公布的演员：男主角Ewan McGregor，女主角Carrie Coon和 Mary Elizabeth Winstead。</p>\n<p>\n\tIn the third season, McGregor will play brothers Emmit and Ray Stussy. &ldquo;Fargo&rdquo; Season 3 will shoot in&nbsp;Calgary with production beginning in January. No premiere date has been set, but the new season will air in 2017.本季，男主角McGregor将一人分饰两角，演一对双胞胎兄弟。《冰血暴》第三季将在1月份在卡尔加里开拍。回归日期未定，不过一定在2017年回归。</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p978568/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p978568\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p978356/\">BBC：动画《你的名字》为何能在中国大获成功</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p975896/\">双语美文：爸爸和妈妈是这样认识的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p977160/\">一夜3起袭击：要付多少代价才能换来世界和平 </a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px