  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://radianttanning.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/TOURS-TO-KERALA-21.jpg\" style=\"color: rgb(16,113,181); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><img alt=\"“no internet”的图片搜索结果\" src=\"http://cdn-media-2.lifehack.org/wp-content/files/2013/10/no-internet-access.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 332px;\" /></a><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThis week's topic:&nbsp; How the Internet changed our lives&nbsp; (90-110 words)<br />\n\tSuggestions:</p>\n<p>\n\t1) Share your story of the Internet</p>\n<p>\n\t2) What have been changed by the Internet?</p>\n<p>\n\t3) Do you benefit from the Internet? Why or why not?</p>\n<p>\n\t4) Anything you would like to write.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHave you ever imagined a life without the Internet? Honestly speaking, even to think about this question is a torture for me due to the fact that our life is massively influenced by the omnipotent Internet. Furthermore, there is no exaggeration to say that a day without the Internet is like a year without the rain. Habits are cultivated. We common people, especially those who live in the front-line cities, are unconsciously accustomed to call cabs, order food as well as purchase through the APPs in the mobile. The Internet and the ensued new technology bring not only convenience but also efficiency to our lives.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/1710196681665/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912806/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912806\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p978356/\">BBC：动画《你的名字》为何能在中国大获成功</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p975896/\">双语美文：爸爸和妈妈是这样认识的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p977160/\">一夜3起袭击：要付多少代价才能换来世界和平 </a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p977133/\">围观：世界上最大狗站高2米多 比姚明还高！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p974492/\">英语数字怎么读</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p977146/\">2016另类圣诞树盘点：老外的创造力真是棒呆！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p972863/\">Quora精选：能不能用数学解释“耳机打结\"？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p975849/\">从中国唐氏弃婴到美国小网红 背后是个辣妈</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p971520/\">2016年12月四级真题&答案汇总</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p978513/\">2016年12月英语六级听力答案&点评：试卷二（付英东版）</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
